The evidence with the title 'Reid wrong on Bush's economic record - factcheck.org ' says Aug 3, 2011  ... Harry Reid falsely claimed that 8 million jobs were lost during the Bush administration . To the contrary, there was a net gain of 1  ... Only about half of those were lost under Bush . The Nevada Democrat also falsely claimed that Bush turned a projected surplus of $ 7 trillion over 10 years into a $14 trillion debt. 
